net.sourceforge.jlevenshtein
Class HashPoint

java.lang.Object
  net.sourceforge.jlevenshtein.HashPoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<HashPoint>
public final class HashPoint
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<HashPoint>, java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable

This class speeds up the comparison process of the Levenshtein class since it requires two value keys for several purposes. Also it is used as return key for the path function that explains the transformation process of two words.

Version:
0.1b
Author:
Rafael W.
